    Kige ga tame

    oshikarazarishi

    Inochi sae

    Nagaku mo gana to

    Omoikeru kana

    For your precious sake, once I thought

    I could die.

    Now, I wish to live with you

    a long, long time.

-- Hokusai and Hiroshige
